    "title": "Hekima",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "hekima",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Hekima hutusaidia kujua jinsi ya kuzungumza na kutenda katika hali mbalimbali. Inaturuhusu kuepuka matatizo na kuyashughulikia yanapotokea. Hekima ni zaidi ya akili tu. Mithali inasema kwamba hata wanyama kama siafu, pimbi wa miamba, nzige, na mijusi ni wenye hekima (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov30:24-Prov30:28\">Mithali 30:24–28</a>). Hawana hekima kwa sababu ya akili kubwa bali kwa sababu wanajua jinsi ya kuishi kwa ustadi.</p><p>Msingi wa hekima ni Mungu. Hakuna hekima bila &quot;kumcha Bwana&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:7\">Mithali 1:7</a>). Hekima inahusishwa na uadilifu na huepuka uovu.</p><p>Kulingana na Mithali, watu wanapata hekima kwa:</p><ul><li><p>Kutafakari na kuchambua maisha (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:6-Prov6:8\">6:6–8</a>)</p></li><li><p>Kujifunza kutoka kwa mafundisho ya jadi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:17-Prov22:21\">22:17–21</a>)</p></li><li><p>Kuelewa makosa (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:1\">12:1</a>)</p></li><li><p>Kitu muhimu zaidi ni kupitia Ufunuo kutoka kwa Mungu (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:7\">1:7</a>)</p></li></ul><p>Kwenye <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:1-1Cor2:16\">1 Wakorintho 1–2</a>, mtume Paulo analinganisha &quot;hekima&quot; ya dunia, ambayo anaiita &quot;upumbavu,&quot; na hekima ya Yesu Kristo. Paulo pia anazungumzia Yesu, “ambaye ndani yake zimefichwa hazina zote za hekima na maarifa” (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:3\">Wakolosai 2:3</a>). Hekima ya Mungu inaonekana katika maisha ya Wakristo kupitia wema wao, unyenyekevu, usafi, na amani (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:13-Jas3:18\">Yakobo 3:13–18</a>).</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut1:13-Deut1:18\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 1:13–18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:5-Deut4:8\">4:5–8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:1-1Kgs3:28\">1 Wafalme 3:1–28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job12:12\">Ayubu 12:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job28:20-Job28:28\">28:20–28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps90:12\">Zaburi 90:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:98\">119:98</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:7\">Mithali 1:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov2:1-Prov2:22\">2:1–22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov30:24-Prov30:28\">30:24–28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:12-Eccl2:16\">Mhubiri 2:12–16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl7:4-Eccl7:19\">7:4–19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:1-Isa11:2\">Isaya 11:1–2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:23-Jer9:24\">Yeremia 9:23–24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:12\">10:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos14:9\">Hosea 14:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:35\">Luka 7:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:18-1Cor3:20\">1 Wakorintho 3:18–20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:5\">Yakobo 1:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:13-Jas3:17\">3:13–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:12\">Ufunuo 7:12</a></p>",
